{"tid":2366061,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"女股神Cathie Wood擬增太空科技ETF ARKX 維珍銀河盤後升14%","createTime":"2021-01-14T08:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:44:36.000Z","uid":323911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35dc795e3551ef0054bd88a4c71554c1b42a15ad","tid":2366061,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210114/JRQD6MOCQNFQHNFWUYKB7R5DQI/?fbclid=IwAR25NmaNhBo20VSjQs_vgfdgb_iwK9gXiMqKQIobfHLwqI07nMQIDGDecVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210114%2FJRQD6MOCQNFQHNFWUYKB7R5DQI%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25NmaNhBo20VSjQs_vgfdgb_iwK9gXiMqKQIobfHLwqI07nMQIDGDecVU&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=7ebf3312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210114%2FJRQD6MOCQNFQHNFWUYKB7R5DQI%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25NmaNhBo20VSjQs_vgfdgb_iwK9gXiMqKQIobfHLwqI07nMQIDGDecVU&h=cb436236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210114/JRQD6MOCQNFQHNFWUYKB7R5DQI/?fbclid=IwAR25NmaNhBo20VSjQs_vgfdgb_iwK9gXiMqKQIobfHLwqI07nMQIDGDecVU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xrH8NsfyllYm6OlHJY_nPXMl82w=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V5E3ATF4XRBKPCYYDH4KO65SEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxrH8NsfyllYm6OlHJY_nPXMl82w%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV5E3ATF4XRBKPCYYDH4KO65SEY.jpg&h=c7bd8431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據CNBC等外媒報導，女股神Cathie Wood旗下投資旗艦Ark Invest擬新增太空科技ETF（Space Exploration ETF） ，股票代號為「ARKX」，並已在星期二（13日）盤後向美國證券交易委員會提交申請文件。<br />\n<br />\n該文件指，ARKX計劃有80%投資將與太空探索及創新有關的企業，包括軌道領域、次軌道領域進行發射、製造、服務或操作平台等業務的企業，如衛星、無人機、電動飛機等。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦會投資為太空科技創造附加價值的企業，包括人工智慧（AI）、機器人、3D 列印、原料與能源儲存等，以及投資農業、網路接取、全球定位系統(GPS)、營建及成像等將因航空業受惠的企業。<br />\n<br />\n雖然Ark Invest尚未公佈ARKX的成分股，但相關概念股盤後飆升。太空旅遊公司維珍銀河（美：SPCE ）盤後升13.93%，通訊雷達與衛星產品服務商Maxar Technologies（美：MAXR）盤後升15.19%，太空ETF Procure（美：UFO）盤後升7.02%。<br />\n<br />\n美國銀行的分析師Ron Epstein指，武漢肺炎未有影響太空科技發展的速度，惟太空產業主要是企業對企業（B2B）或企業對政府（B2G），因此復甦速度較一般快。他又估計太空產業會由2019年的4,240 億美元，增至2030年1.4萬億美元，追近全球旅遊業1.5萬億美元的規模。"},{"pid":"0c5578161924ba895ae4302149f827c7672adc4d","tid":2366061,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fafffb9aa2d4d25fd860ba38b927380770ba32","tid":2366061,"uid":271322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:33:25.000Z","msg":"進軍外太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d811f0a2714066deeb632cf2093c57e7e931fa","tid":2366061,"uid":8717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"對於契媽既所有產品, 本人確信買入"},{"pid":"f2e7122a5f00c91128e6fd64ca3c508cb086aab8","tid":2366061,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"完全冇睇字我剩係知道ARKX ＝買買買並持有至死"},{"pid":"aa83bdc175c3ad3158635d6ceec72e1b6a0fb924","tid":2366061,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2e7122a5f00c91128e6fd64ca3c508cb086aab8","tid":2366061,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"完全冇睇字我剩係知道ARKX ＝買買買並持有至死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"ark字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2433b8cfbf2288734d1b9cd5870049fe40738c69","tid":2366061,"uid":175649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa83bdc175c3ad3158635d6ceec72e1b6a0fb924","tid":2366061,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2e7122a5f00c9